          "reviewBody": "Chennai Public School - Thirumazhisai Chennai,Tamil Nadu 600124\n\nI had unfavorable feedback at the cost of one year fee & worsening the study base of my children.\n\nMost Teachers are freshers. Soon, you will find absent & then the new one. The teacher seems low salaried members, appears there for training. I have observed frequently they resign job for married life or soon lands a better school.\n\nTwo distinctive AVATR to assess in this school is Mr. Madan - Chief Warden, Mr. Surya Murthy - Accounts Manager and their insubordination with the Principal. Typical politics entertained by poor management. By the way, you never get a chance to meet anybody from Management.\n\nSchool APP for monitoring performance is not updated. No proper circular to inform the parents except school fee collection.\n\nThe school has open land for sake of playground. No sports gadget are equipped.\n\nThe school has a power transmission corridor, wire passing through in the children pay area. This is the disaster, how come the school authority of TN  left children's life to a high potential hazard.\n\nOther shabby findings\nAC Room is offered at an additional payment. Most staff member will sleep with their mobile phone ON, Night shows played in children rooms. AC is rational to use only!\n\nPoor laundry service. Unclean Bathroom, limited hot water, and unhygienic condition are added complement.\n\nWhen it comes to food, poor quality. It was tearful for my mistake in joining here.\n\nGood menus are served during lunch time to facilitate day time staff has a good food.\n\nLow profile food items are pushed in the evening. Evening snacks are junk are nothing but pure junk.\n\nSad to see, the Good portion of food, selected chicken pieces will be collected first by the Chief Warden - Shame on him ! & staff Group as per hierarchy. Now, the left out will be served to the poor children on a first come - first serve basis.\n\nThe normal parent will have heart burns!\n\nService of dropping to airport and railway station is denied.\n\nFrequent penalty for broken glass in hostel, cupboard maintenance are part of gift.\nItem get stolen by (staff) co student are common practice.\n\nTV time has no discipline. Remote will be in the hand of children.\n\nNo teacher or guidance provided in the school study hours.\n\nUniforms were issued in the middle of the academic.\n\nBrowse The Hindu newspaper for media coverage about CHOKKIDHANI INCIDENT - The worst day trip,  Teacher had fun time while Children got locked in the room & beaten up !\n\nLifetime lesson for my poor workout and choosing this school.",
